PROBLEM: 'The War of '$1812$' started with a declaration of war on Thursday, June '$18$', '$1812$'. The peace treaty to end the war was signed '$919$' days later, on December '$24$', '$1814$'. On what day of the week was the treaty signed? \n'
=======
CHOICES:
[A]: \text{Friday}
[B]: \text{Saturday}
[C]: \text{Sunday}
[D]: \text{Monday}
[E]: \text{Tuesday}

PROBLEM: 'What is the area of the region enclosed by the graph of the equation '$x^2+y^2=|x|+|y|?$'\n'
=======
CHOICES:
[A]: \pi+\sqrt{2}
[B]: \pi+2
[C]: \pi+2\sqrt{2}
[D]: 2\pi+\sqrt{2}
[E]: 2\pi+2\sqrt{2}

PROBLEM: 'Tom, Dick, and Harry are playing a game. Starting at the same time, each of them flips a fair coin repeatedly until he gets his first head, at which point he stops. What is the probability that all three flip their coins the same number of times?\n'
=======
CHOICES:
[A]: \frac{1}{8}
[B]: \frac{1}{7}
[C]: \frac{1}{6}
[D]: \frac{1}{4}
[E]: \frac{1}{3}

PROBLEM: 'Let '$ABCD$' be a unit square. Let '$Q_1$' be the midpoint of '$\overline{CD}$'. For '$i=1,2,\dots,$' let '$P_i$' be the intersection of '$\overline{AQ_i}$' and '$\overline{BD}$', and let '$Q_{i+1}$' be the foot of the perpendicular from '$P_i$' to '$\overline{CD}$'. What is \n'\[\sum_{i=1}^{\infty} \text{Area of } \triangle DQ_i P_i \, ?\]'\n'
=======
CHOICES:
[A]: \frac{1}{6}
[B]: \frac{1}{4}
[C]: \frac{1}{3}
[D]: \frac{1}{2}
[E]: 1
